'''亚卤酸根'''，或称'''亚卤酸盐''',<ref>{{cite book |last1=Holleman |first1=A. F. |last2=Wiberg |first2=Egon |last3=Wiberg |first3=Nils |title=Inorganic Chemistry |date=2001 |publisher=Academic Press |location=Web |isbn=9780123526519 |page=439 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Mtth5g59dEIC&printsec=frontcover&dq=isbn:0123526515&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj3_6-spJLhAhWH1IMKHTaCDosQuwUILTAA&pg=PA439#v=onepage&q&f=false |accessdate=21 March 2019 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922071045/https://books.google.com/books?id=Mtth5g59dEIC&printsec=frontcover&dq=isbn:0123526515&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj3_6-spJLhAhWH1IMKHTaCDosQuwUILTAA&pg=PA439#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>是一种[[含氧酸根|含氧酸根]]，拥有+3[[氧化态|氧化态]]的[[卤素|卤素]]原子。 它是[[亚卤酸|亚卤酸]]的共轭碱。 已知的亚卤酸根有[[亚氯酸根|亚氯酸根]]，[[亚溴酸根|亚溴酸根]]和[[亚碘酸根|亚碘酸根]]。

==用处==
氧化亚卤酸盐时，它会形成卤素二氧化物:
:[[亚氯酸钠|5NaClO<sub>2</sub>]] + [[盐酸|4HCl]] → [[氯化钠|5NaCl]] + [[二氧化氯|4{{chem]] + [[水|2H<sub>2</sub>O]]
:[[亚溴酸盐|BrO<sub>2</sub><sup>−</sup>]] + [[溴酸|HBrO<sub>3</sub> + H<sup>+</sup>]] → [[二氧化溴|2 {{chem]]  + [[水|H<sub>2</sub>O]]
这是获取漂白剂二氧化氯的一种方法。

==稳定性==
加热亚氯酸盐时，它们会分解甚至爆炸。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Holleman |first1=A. F. |last2=Wiberg |first2=Egon |last3=Wiberg |first3=Nils |title=Inorganic Chemistry |date=2001 |publisher=Academic Press |location=Web |isbn=9780123526519 |page=445 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Mtth5g59dEIC&printsec=frontcover&dq=isbn:0123526515&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj3_6-spJLhAhWH1IMKHTaCDosQuwUILTAA&pg=PA445#v=onepage&q&f=false |accessdate=21 March 2019 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920200146/https://books.google.com/books?id=Mtth5g59dEIC&printsec=frontcover&dq=isbn:0123526515&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj3_6-spJLhAhWH1IMKHTaCDosQuwUILTAA&pg=PA445#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>人们目前已经分离出一些亚溴酸盐，不过没有分离出亚碘酸盐。<ref>Egon Wiberg, Arnold Frederick Holleman (2001) ''Inorganic Chemistry'', Elsevier {{ISBN|0-12-352651-5}}</ref>

